research_municipality_step.notes: The City of Crockett operates with a Council-Manager form of Home Rule government, which aligns with a mayor-council system. Dr. Ianthia Fisher was re-elected as Mayor in May 2023. Mike Marsh serves as Mayor Pro Tem and Council Member for Precinct 5. Dennis Ivey is the Council Member for Precinct 1. NaTrenia Hicks is the Council Member for Precinct 3. Elbert Johnson is the Council Member for Precinct 4. There is conflicting information regarding the Council Member for Precinct 2; some sources from 2023, 2024, and 2025 meeting agendas list Darrell Jones, while the official city website and TML directory list Christopher Price. Christopher Price has been used based on the official directory and city website listings.
